import React from "react";

import Header from "../../../../components/Header";
import {
  Container,
  Column,
  Card,
  Form,
  WrapperInput,
  SmallLabel,
  CardInput,
  Row,
  CVVInput,
  DateInput,
  Input,
  Buttons,
  Back,
  Button,
  CreditCard,
} from "./styles";

function DesktopForm() {
  return (
    <Container>
      <Column>
        <Card />
      </Column>
      <Column>
        <Form>
          <WrapperInput>
            <SmallLabel>número do cartão</SmallLabel>
            <CardInput placeholder="0000 0000 0000 0000" />
          </WrapperInput>
          <Row marginTop={30}>
            <WrapperInput>
              <SmallLabel>CVV</SmallLabel>
              <CVVInput placeholder="000" />
            </WrapperInput>
            <WrapperInput>
              <SmallLabel>expiração</SmallLabel>
              <DateInput placeholder="00/0000" />
            </WrapperInput>
          </Row>
          <WrapperInput marginTop={30}>
            <SmallLabel>nome do proprietário</SmallLabel>
            <Input placeholder="nome do proprietário" />
          </WrapperInput>
        </Form>
      </Column>
      <Buttons>
        <Back>voltar</Back>
        <Button>
          <CreditCard />
        </Button>
      </Buttons>
    </Container>
  );
}

export default DesktopForm;
